#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "KrViewer: &krusader;'s internal viewer-editor"
msgstr "KrViewer: &krusader;-jev interni pregledovalnik-urejevalnik"

#. Tag: primary
#: viewer-editor.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Viewer</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Gledalnik</primary>"

#. Tag: seealso
#: viewer-editor.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "<seealso>Editor</seealso>"
msgstr "<seealso>Urejevalnik</seealso>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing &Enter; on a selected file <emphasis>opens the file with the "
"associated application</emphasis>. The editor-viewer is tabbed, configure it "
"on the <link linkend=\"konfig-general\">Konfigurator General page</link>"
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom &Enter; na izbrani datoteki <emphasis>odpre datoteko s povezano "
"aplikacijo</emphasis>. Urejevalnik-pregledovalnik je z zavihki, "
"konfigurirajte ga na <link linkend=\"konfig-general\">strani Konfigurator "
"General</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Viewer</title>"
msgstr "<title>Gledalnik</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view a file as fast as possible according to its type, just put it under "
"the cursor and press <keycap>F3</keycap>. &krusader;'s internal viewer is "
"actually a part of &konqueror;, which can basically view every file type "
"viewable by &konqueror; (&eg; display pictures, play music, show the content "
"of an archive). This is called the 'Generic viewer', for which you need to "
"configure the &MIME; types."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati datoteko čim hitreje glede na njeno vrsto, jo samo "
"postavite pod kazalec in pritisnite <keycap>F3</keycap>. Notranji "
"pregledovalnik &krusader; je pravzaprav del &konqueror;ja, ki si lahko v "
"bistvu ogleda vsako vrsto datoteke, ki si jo lahko ogleda &konqueror; (&eg; "
"prikaz slik, predvajanje glasbe, prikaz vsebine arhiva). To se imenuje "
"'generični pregledovalnik', za katerega morate konfigurirati &MIME; vrste."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The viewer works as follows: <itemizedlist> <listitem> <para>It tries to "
"view the file with the <emphasis>'Generic viewer'.</emphasis></para> </"
"listitem> <listitem> <para>When the file type (&MIME; type) cannot be "
"determined or when a file (&eg; a binary) does not have an associated "
"action, it disables the 'generic viewer'. The file is treated as a text "
"file, which is the <emphasis>'Text viewer'</emphasis>.</para> </listitem> "
"<listitem> <para>The user can change in the <link linkend="
"\"kredit_krviewer_menu\">KrViewer menu</link> between: 'Generic viewer' (if "
"available), 'Text viewer' and <emphasis>'Hex viewer'</emphasis>.</para> </"
"listitem> </itemizedlist>You can configure the default viewer mode on the "
"<link linkend=\"konfig-general\">Konfigurator General page</link> ."
msgstr ""
"Pregledovalnik deluje na naslednji način: <itemizedlist> <listitem> "
"<para>Datoteko si poskuša ogledati z <emphasis>'generičnim pregledovalnikom'."
"</emphasis></para> </listitem> <listitem> <para>Ko vrste datoteke (&MIME; "
"vrsta) ni mogoče določiti ali ko datoteka (&eg; dvojiška) nima povezanega "
"dejanja, onemogoči 'generični pregledovalnik'. Datoteka se obravnava kot "
"besedilna datoteka, ki je <emphasis>'Pregledovalnik besedil'</emphasis>.</"
"para> </listitem> <listitem> <para>Uporabnik lahko spremeni v <link linkend="
"\"kredit_krviewer_menu\">Meni KrViewer</link> med: 'Generični "
"pregledovalnik' (če je na voljo), 'Pregledovalnik besedila' in "
"<emphasis>'Šestnajstiški pregledovalnik'</emphasis>.</para> </listitem> </"
"itemizedlist>Lahko konfigurirajte privzeti način pregledovalnika na <link "
"linkend=\"konfig-general\">strani Konfigurator General</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> views a "
"&URL; on demand, &eg;:"
msgstr ""
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> si ogleda "
"&URL; na zahtevo, &eg;:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput> <command>man:/</command> </userinput>views the manpages."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>man:/</command> </userinput>ogleda strani s priročniki."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput> <command>man:/</command><replaceable>krusader</replaceable> </"
"userinput>views manpage of &krusader;."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>man:/</command><replaceable>krusader</replaceable> </"
"userinput>ogled strani priročnika za &krusader;."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput> <command>info:/</command> </userinput>views the infopages."
msgstr "<userinput> <command>info:/</command> </userinput>ogleda infostrani."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput> <command>https://</command><replaceable>krusader.org</"
"replaceable> </userinput>views a webpage."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>https://</command><replaceable>krusader.org</"
"replaceable> </userinput>ogleda spletno stran."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput> <command>ftp://</command><replaceable>ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/</"
"replaceable> </userinput>views a &FTP; server."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>ftp://</command><replaceable>ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/</"
"replaceable> </userinput>ogleda &FTP; strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput> <command>sftp://</command><replaceable>sftp.foo/</replaceable> </"
"userinput>views a secure &FTP; server."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>sftp://</command><replaceable>sftp.foo/</replaceable> </"
"userinput>ogleda varno &FTP; strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput> <command>file:/</command><replaceable>home/frank</replaceable> </"
"userinput>views Frank's home folder."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>datoteka:/</command><replaceable>home/frank</"
"replaceable> </userinput>ogleda Frankovo domačo mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput> <command>tar:/</command><replaceable>home/frank/archive.tar.gz/</"
"replaceable> </userinput>opens content browser window for the <literal role="
"\"extension\">tar.gz</literal> archive."
msgstr ""
"<userinput> <command>tar:/</command><replaceable>home/frank/archive.tar.gz/</"
"replaceable> </userinput>odpre okno brskalnika vsebine za <literal role="
"\"extension\">tar. gz</literal> arhiv."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"KrViewer can have the following menus: <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-file"
"\">File</link>, <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-edit\">Edit</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"katepart-menu-view\">View</link>, <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-"
"settings\">Settings</link> and <link linkend=\"kredit_krviewer_menu"
"\">Krviewer</link>, depending on which file type is viewed. They will be "
"discussed in the <link linkend=\"kredit\">Editor section</link>. The "
"internal viewer can follow links on &HTML; pages. With <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> the viewer can start "
"&krusader;'s internal editor (which is basically the same application)."
msgstr ""
"KrViewer ima lahko naslednje menije: <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-file"
"\">Datoteka</link>, <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-edit\">Uredi</link>, <link "
"linkend=\"katepart-menu-view\">Pogled</link>, <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-"
"settings\">Nastavitve</link> in <link linkend=\"kredit_krviewer_menu"
"\">Krviewer</link>, odvisno od tega, katera vrsta datoteke je prikazana . O "
"njih bomo razpravljali v <link linkend=\"kredit\">razdelku urejevalnika</"
"link>. Notranji pregledovalnik lahko sledi povezavam na &HTML; strani. Z "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> lahko "
"pregledovalnik zažene notranji urejevalnik &krusader; (ki je v bistvu ista "
"aplikacija)."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The embedded viewer is not written by us, it is supplied via &kde-"
"frameworks; and KIO Slaves. We cannot and do not want to change it, using "
"these libraries reduces the amount of written code. So we do not have to "
"reinvent the wheel ;-)"
msgstr ""
"Vdelanega pregledovalnika nismo napisali mi, dobavljen je prek &kde-"
"frameworks; in KIO Sužnji. Ne moremo in nočemo ga spremeniti, uporaba teh "
"knjižnic zmanjša količino napisane kode. Torej nam ni treba znova izumljati "
"kolesa ;-)"

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Editor</title>"
msgstr "<title>Urejevalnik</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: viewer-editor.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Editor</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Urejevalnik</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader;'s internal editor has almost everything that you can expect of an "
"editor. Editing is similar to viewing but with the <keycap>F4</keycap> key. "
"The default editor is &krusader;'s internal editor. You can change the "
"default editor in the <link linkend=\"konfig-general\">Konfigurator General "
"page</link>, if you prefer to use an external editor."
msgstr ""
"Notranji urejevalnik &krusader; ima skoraj vse, kar lahko pričakujete od "
"urejevalnika. Urejanje je podobno ogledovanju, vendar s tipko <keycap>F4</"
"keycap>. Privzeti urejevalnik je notranji urejevalnik &krusader;. Privzeti "
"urejevalnik lahko spremenite na <link linkend=\"konfig-general\">strani "
"Konfigurator General</link>, če raje uporabljate zunanji urejevalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you use &krusader;'s internal editor for the first time, it is "
"recommended to look at each section of the <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-"
"settings\">Settings</link> menu, and configure it the way you want it."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič uporabljate notranji urejevalnik &krusader;, je priporočljivo, da "
"si ogledate vsak razdelek v meniju <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-settings"
"\">Nastavitve</link> in ga konfigurirate tako, kot želite to."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu overview"
msgstr "Pregled menija"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are different menus and menu items in simple and advanced mode. The "
"advanced mode is enabled by checking the option <link linkend=\"katepart-"
"appearance\"> Enable power user mode (&kde; 3 mode)</link> on the "
"<guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> page in &kappname;s settings."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo različni meniji in menijski elementi v preprostem in naprednem "
"načinu. Napredni način je omogočen tako, da označite možnost <link linkend="
"\"katepart-appearance\"> Omogoči napredni uporabniški način (&kde; 3 način)</"
"link> na strani <guilabel>Videz</guilabel> v nastavitvah &kappname;."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This saves the current document. If there has already been a save of the "
"document then this will overwrite the previously saved file without asking "
"for the user's consent. If it is the first save of a new document the save "
"as dialog (described below) will be invoked."
msgstr ""
"To shrani trenutni dokument. Če je dokument že bil shranjen, bo to prepisalo "
"predhodno shranjeno datoteko, ne da bi uporabnik vprašal za soglasje. Če gre "
"za prvo shranjevanje novega dokumenta, se odpre pogovorno okno za "
"shranjevanje kot (opisano spodaj)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani kot ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "This allows a document to be saved with a new file name."
msgstr "To omogoča shranjevanje dokumenta z novim imenom datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Znova naloži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reloads the active file from disk. This command is useful if another program "
"or process has changed the file while you have it open in &kappname;."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno naloži aktivno datoteko z diska. Ta ukaz je uporaben, če je drug "
"program ali proces spremenil datoteko, medtem ko jo imate odprto v "
"&kappname;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a simple print dialog allowing the user to specify what, where, and "
"how to print."
msgstr ""
"Odpre preprosto pogovorno okno za tiskanje, ki uporabniku omogoča, da "
"določi, kaj, kje in kako naj tiska."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export as &HTML;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvozi kot &HTML;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Export your file in &HTML; format so your document can be viewed as a web "
"page. This item is only displayed when the plugin <guilabel>Exporter</"
"guilabel> is loaded."
msgstr ""
"Izvozite datoteko v &HTML; tako da si lahko dokument ogledate kot spletno "
"stran. Ta element je prikazan le, ko je naložen vtičnik <guilabel>Izvoznik</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to eliminate or reverse the most recent user action or "
"operation."
msgstr ""
"To se uporablja za odstranitev ali razveljavitev zadnjega dejanja ali "
"operacije uporabnika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Redo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will reverse the most recent change (if any) made using Undo"
msgstr ""
"S tem boste razveljavili najnovejšo spremembo (če obstaja), narejeno s "
"funkcijo Razveljavi"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izreži</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command deletes the current selection and places it on the clipboard. "
"The clipboard is a feature that works invisibly to provide a way to transfer "
"data between applications."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz izbriše trenutni izbor in ga postavi v odložišče. Odložišče je "
"funkcija, ki deluje nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This copies the currently selected text to the clipboard so that it may be "
"pasted elsewhere. The clipboard is a feature that works invisibly to provide "
"a way to transfer data between applications."
msgstr ""
"S tem kopirate trenutno izbrano besedilo v odložišče, da ga lahko prilepite "
"drugam. Odložišče je funkcija, ki deluje nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov "
"med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will insert the contents of the clipboard at the cursor position. The "
"clipboard is a feature that works invisibly to provide a way to transfer "
"data between applications."
msgstr ""
"To bo vstavilo vsebino odložišča na položaj kazalke. Odložišče je funkcija, "
"ki deluje nevidno in omogoča prenos podatkov med aplikacijami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy as &HTML;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj kot &HTML;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This copies the currently selected text to the clipboard as &HTML;. This "
"item is only displayed when the plugin <guilabel>Exporter</guilabel> is "
"loaded."
msgstr ""
"To kopira trenutno izbrano besedilo v odložišče kot &HTML;. Ta element je "
"prikazan le, ko je naložen vtičnik <guilabel>Izvoznik</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izberi vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will select the entire document. This could be very useful for copying "
"the entire file to another application."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste izbrali celoten dokument. To je lahko zelo koristno za kopiranje "
"celotne datoteke v drugo aplikacijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Deselect</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prekliči izbiro</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deselects the selected text in the editor if any."
msgstr "Prekliče izbiro izbranega besedila v urejevalniku, če obstaja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Block Selection "
"Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Blokiraj način "
"izbire</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles Selection Mode. When the Selection Mode is <guilabel>BLOCK</"
"guilabel>, you can make vertical selections, &eg; select column 5 to 10 in "
"lines 9 to 15. The status bar shows the current state of the Selection Mode, "
"either <guilabel>BLOCK</guilabel> or <guilabel>LINE</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi način izbire. Ko je način izbire <guilabel>BLOKIRAJ</guilabel>, "
"lahko izbirate navpično, &eg; izberite stolpec od 5 do 10 v vrsticah od 9 do "
"15. Statusna vrstica prikazuje trenutno stanje izbirnega načina, bodisi "
"<guilabel>BLOKIRAJ</guilabel> ali <guilabel>VRSTICA</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Meta;&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>VI input Mode</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Meta;&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vnosni način VI</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch to a vi-like, modal editing mode. This mode supports the most used "
"commands and motions from vim's normal and visual mode and has an optional "
"vi mode statusbar. This status bar shows commands while they are being "
"entered, output from commands and the current mode.The behavior of this mode "
"can be configured in the <link linkend=\"katepart-pref-edit-vi-input-mode"
"\">Vi Input Mode</link> section of the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> page in "
"&kappname;'s settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite na modalni način urejanja, podoben vi. Ta način podpira "
"najpogosteje uporabljene ukaze in gibe iz normalnega in vizualnega načina "
"vim in ima izbirno statusno vrstico načina vi. Ta statusna vrstica prikazuje "
"ukaze med vnašanjem, izhod iz ukazov in trenutni način. Vedenje tega načina "
"je mogoče konfigurirati v <link linkend=\"katepart-pref-edit-vi-input-mode"
"\">Vi Input Mode </link> na strani <guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel> v "
"pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami &kappname;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ins;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Overwrite Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ins;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Način prepisovanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the Insert/Overwrite modes. When the mode is <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel>, you insert characters where the cursor is. When the mode is "
"<guilabel>OVR</guilabel>, writing characters will replace the current "
"characters if your cursor is positioned before any character. The status bar "
"shows the current state of the Overwrite Mode, either <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>OVR</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi med načini Vstavljanje/Prepisovanje. Ko je način <guilabel>INS</"
"guilabel>, vstavite znake tam, kjer je kazalec. Ko je način <guilabel>OVR</"
"guilabel>, bodo pisni znaki nadomestili trenutne znake, če je vaš kazalec "
"postavljen pred kateri koli znak. Statusna vrstica prikazuje trenutno stanje "
"načina prepisovanja, <guilabel>INS</guilabel> ali <guilabel>OVR</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the incremental search bar at the bottom of the editor window. On "
"the left side of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, followed "
"by a small text box for entering the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"To odpre vrstico za postopno iskanje na dnu okna urejevalnika. Na levi "
"strani vrstice je gumb z ikono za zapiranje vrstice, ki mu sledi majhno "
"besedilno polje za vnos iskalnega vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start entering characters of your search pattern, the search starts "
"immediately. If there is a match in the text this is highlighted and the "
"background color of the entry field changes to light green. If the search "
"pattern does not match any string in the text, this is indicated by a light "
"red background color of the entry field and <guilabel>Not found</guilabel> "
"is displayed at the right side of the bar."
msgstr ""
"Ko začnete vnašati znake svojega iskalnega vzorca, se iskanje začne takoj. "
"Če se besedilo ujema, je to označeno in barva ozadja vnosnega polja se "
"spremeni v svetlo zeleno. Če se iskalni vzorec ne ujema z nobenim nizom v "
"besedilu, je to označeno s svetlo rdečo barvo ozadja vnosnega polja in na "
"desni strani vrstice je prikazano <guilabel>Ni najdeno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:404 viewer-editor.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>Next</guilabel> or <guilabel>Previous</guilabel> button to "
"jump to the next or previous match in the document."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite gumb <guilabel>Naprej</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Prejšnji</guilabel> "
"za skok na naslednje ali prejšnje ujemanje v dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose whether the search should be case sensitive. Selecting "
"<guilabel>Match Case</guilabel> will limit finds to entries that match the "
"case (upper or lower) of each of the characters in the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko, ali naj iskanje razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami. Če "
"izberete <guilabel>Ujemi velike in male črke</guilabel>, boste omejili "
"iskanje na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali malimi črkami vsakega od "
"znakov v iskalnem vzorcu."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the button with a green arrow icon at the right side of the "
"incremental search bar to switch to the power search and replace bar."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb z ikono zelene puščice na desni strani vrstice za "
"inkrementalno iskanje, da preklopite na vrstico za zmogljivo iskanje in "
"zamenjavo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi naslednje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This repeats the last find operation, if any, without calling the "
"incremental search bar."
msgstr ""
"To ponovi zadnjo operacijo iskanja, če obstaja, brez klica prirastne iskalne "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F3</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poišči prejšnje</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This repeats the last find operation, if any, without calling the "
"incremental search bar, and searching backwards instead of forwards through "
"the document."
msgstr ""
"To ponovi zadnjo operacijo iskanja, če obstaja, brez klica prirastne iskalne "
"vrstice in iskanja nazaj namesto naprej po dokumentu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Replace...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zamenjaj ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command opens the power search and replace bar. On the upper left side "
"of the bar is a button with an icon to close the bar, followed by a small "
"text box for entering the search pattern."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz odpre vrstico za iskanje in zamenjavo. Na zgornji levi strani "
"vrstice je gumb z ikono za zapiranje vrstice, ki mu sledi majhno besedilno "
"polje za vnos iskalnega vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control the search mode by selecting <guilabel>Plain text</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Whole words</guilabel>, <guilabel>Escape sequences</"
"guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular expression</guilabel> from the drop down box."
msgstr ""
"Način iskanja lahko nadzirate tako, da na padajočem meniju izberete "
"<guilabel>Navadno besedilo</guilabel>, <guilabel>Cele besede</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Ubežna zaporedja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Regularni izraz</"
"guilabel> navzdol škatla. "

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Escape sequences</guilabel> or <guilabel>Regular expression</"
"guilabel> are selected, the <guibutton>Add...</guibutton> menuitem at the "
"bottom of the context menu of the text boxes will be enabled and allows you "
"to add escape sequences or regular expression items to the search or replace "
"pattern from predefined lists."
msgstr ""
"Če so izbrana <guilabel>Ubežna zaporedja</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Regularni "
"izraz</guilabel>, bo omogočen menijski element <guibutton>Dodaj ...</"
"guibutton> na dnu priročnega menija besedilnih polj in vam omogoča dodajanje "
"ubežnih zaporedij ali postavk regularnega izraza v vzorec iskanja ali "
"zamenjave iz vnaprej določenih seznamov."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the text to replace with in the text box labeled <guilabel>Replace</"
"guilabel> and click the <guibutton>Replace</guibutton> button to replace "
"only the highlighted text or the <guibutton>Replace All</guibutton> button "
"to replace the search text in the whole document."
msgstr ""
"V besedilno polje z oznako <guilabel>Zamenjaj</guilabel> vnesite besedilo, s "
"katerim želite zamenjati, in kliknite gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj</guibutton>, "
"da zamenjate samo označeno besedilo, ali gumb <guibutton>Zamenjaj vse</"
"guibutton>, da zamenjajte iskalno besedilo v celotnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can modify the search and replace behavior by selecting different "
"options at the bottom of the bar. Selecting <guilabel>Match Case</guilabel> "
"will limit finds to entries that match the case (upper or lower) of each of "
"the characters in the search pattern. <guilabel>Selection Only</guilabel> "
"will search and replace within the current selection only. The "
"<guilabel>Find All</guilabel> button highlights all matches in the document "
"and shows the number of found matches in a small popup."
msgstr ""
"Obnašanje iskanja in zamenjave lahko spremenite tako, da izberete različne "
"možnosti na dnu vrstice. Če izberete <guilabel>Ujemi velike in male črke</"
"guilabel>, boste omejili iskanje na vnose, ki se ujemajo z velikimi ali "
"malimi črkami vsakega od znakov v iskalnem vzorcu. <guilabel>Samo izbor</"
"guilabel> bo iskal in zamenjal samo znotraj trenutnega izbora. Gumb "
"<guilabel>Najdi vse</guilabel> označi vse zadetke v dokumentu in prikaže "
"število najdenih zadetkov v majhnem pojavnem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the button with a green arrow icon at the right side of the power "
"search and replace bar to switch to the incremental search bar."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb z ikono zelene puščice na desni strani močne vrstice za "
"iskanje in zamenjavo, da preklopite na vrstico za postopno iskanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Selected</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Poišči izbrano</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finds next occurrence of selected text."
msgstr "Poišče naslednjo pojavitev izbranega besedila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>H</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Selected "
"Backwards</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>H</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Poišči izbrano "
"nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finds previous occurrence of selected text."
msgstr "Poišče prejšnjo pojavitev izbranega besedila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Line...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na vrstico ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the goto line bar at the bottom of the window which is used to "
"have the cursor jump to a particular line (specified by number) in the "
"document. The line number may be entered directly into the text box or "
"graphically by clicking on the up or down arrow spin controls at the side of "
"the text box. The little up arrow will increase the line number and the down "
"arrow decrease it. Close the bar with a click on the button with an icon on "
"the left side of the bar."
msgstr ""
"To odpre vrstico za prehod na vrstico na dnu okna, ki se uporablja za skok "
"kazalca na določeno vrstico (določeno s številko) v dokumentu. Številko "
"vrstice lahko vnesete neposredno v besedilno polje ali grafično s klikom na "
"puščico gor ali dol ob strani besedilnega polja. Majhna puščica navzgor "
"poveča številko vrstice, puščica navzdol pa zmanjša. Vrstico zapremo s "
"klikom na gumb z ikono na levi strani vrstice."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>View</guimenu> menu allows you to manage settings specific to "
"the active editor, and to manage frames."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> vam omogoča upravljanje nastavitev, "
"specifičnih za aktivni urejevalnik, in upravljanje okvirjev."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Window</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo okno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create another window containing the current document. All changes to the "
"document in one window are reflected in the other window and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite drugo okno s trenutnim dokumentom. Vse spremembe dokumenta v enem "
"oknu se odražajo v drugem oknu in obratno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Switch to Command Line</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F7</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preklopi na ukazno vrstico</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the Katepart command line at the bottom of the window. In the "
"command line, type <userinput>help</userinput> to get help and "
"<userinput>help list</userinput> to get a list of commands."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže ukazno vrstico Katepart na dnu okna. V ukazno vrstico vnesite "
"<userinput>pomoč</userinput>, da dobite pomoč, in <userinput>seznam pomoči</"
"userinput>, da dobite seznam ukazov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show the Javascript Console</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži konzolo Javascript</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens a tool view that allows you to run Javascript code interactively. "
"For more information, see <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-"
"scripting.html\">Extending &kate; with Scripts</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"To odpre pogled orodja, ki vam omogoča interaktivno izvajanje kode "
"Javascript. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-"
"editing-tools-scripting.html\">Razširitev &kate; s skripti</ulink>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Schema</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Shema</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select a font schema."
msgstr "Izberite shemo pisave."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dynamic Word Wrap</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F10</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dinamični prelom besed</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid "The text lines will be wrapped at the view border on the screen."
msgstr "Besedilne vrstice bodo obrobljene ob meji pogleda na zaslonu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Dynamic Word Wrap Indicators</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Kazalniki dinamičnega preloma besed</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose when and how the dynamic word wrap indicators should be displayed. "
"This is only available if the <guilabel>Dynamic Word Wrap</guilabel> option "
"is checked."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kdaj in kako naj bodo prikazani indikatorji dinamičnega preloma "
"besed. To je na voljo le, če je označena možnost <guilabel>Dinamični prelom "
"besed</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Static Word Wrap Marker</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži statični marker za prelom "
"besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:634 viewer-editor.docbook:1707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a vertical line will be drawn at the word wrap "
"column as defined in the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the Editing "
"tab. Please note that the word wrap marker is only drawn if you use a fixed "
"pitch font."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo na stolpcu za prelom besed narisana navpična "
"črta, kot je definirano v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"Zavihek za urejanje. Upoštevajte, da je oznaka za prelom besed narisana le, "
"če uporabljate pisavo s fiksno višino."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F6</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži obrobo ikone</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle item. Setting it on checked will make the Icon Border "
"visible in the left side of the active editor, and vice versa. The Icon "
"Border indicates the positions of the marked lines in the editor."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopni element. Če je označeno, bo obroba ikone vidna na levi "
"strani aktivnega urejevalnika in obratno. Obroba ikone označuje položaje "
"označenih vrstic v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F11</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži številke vrstic</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a toggle Item. Setting it on checked will make a pane displaying the "
"line numbers of the document visible in the left border of the active "
"editor, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"To je preklopni element. Če ga nastavite na označeno, bo podokno, ki "
"prikazuje številke vrstic dokumenta, vidno na levem robu aktivnega "
"urejevalnika in obratno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show Scrollbar Marks</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikaži oznake drsnega traku</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, the view will show marks on the vertical "
"scrollbar. The marks are equivalent to the marks on the <link linkend="
"\"katepart-menu-view-show-icon-border\">Icon Border</link>."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo v pogledu prikazane oznake na navpičnem "
"drsnem traku. Oznake so enakovredne oznakam na <link linkend=\"katepart-menu-"
"view-show-icon-border\">obrobi ikone</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Folding Markers</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži zložljive oznake</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "If this option is checked, the marks for code folding will be shown."
msgstr "Če je ta možnost označena, bodo prikazane oznake za zlaganje kode."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Code Folding</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zgibanje kode</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options pertain to <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-tools-"
"code-folding.html\">code folding</ulink>:"
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti se nanašajo na <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/advanced-editing-"
"tools-code-folding.html\">zlaganje kode</ulink>:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Show Folding Markers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Pokaži zložljive oznake</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the display of the folding marker pane in the left side of the view."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi prikaz zložljivega podokna označevalcev na levi strani pogleda."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: viewer-editor.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fold Current Node"
msgstr "Zloži trenutno vozlišče"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collapse the region that contains the cursor."
msgstr "Strni območje, ki vsebuje kazalec."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: viewer-editor.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unfold Current Node"
msgstr "Razgrni trenutno vozlišče"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand the region that contains the cursor."
msgstr "Razširite območje, ki vsebuje kazalec."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Fold Toplevel Nodes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>-</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenuitem>Zloži vozlišča najvišje ravni</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Collapse all toplevel regions in the document. Click on the right pointing "
"triangle to expand all toplevel regions."
msgstr ""
"Strni vse regije najvišje ravni v dokumentu. Kliknite desni trikotnik, da "
"razširite vse regije najvišje ravni."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: viewer-editor.docbook:757
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enlarge Font"
msgstr "Povečaj pisavo"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid "This increases the display font size."
msgstr "To poveča velikost pisave na zaslonu."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: viewer-editor.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shrink Font"
msgstr "Skrči pisavo"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid "This decreases the display font size."
msgstr "To zmanjša velikost pisave na zaslonu."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "Meni z zaznamki"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Set Bookmark</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>B</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nastavi zaznamek</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets or removes a bookmark in the current line of the active document. (If "
"it is there, it is removed, otherwise one is set)."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi ali odstrani zaznamek v trenutni vrstici aktivnega dokumenta. (Če je "
"tam, se odstrani, drugače se nastavi eno)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear All Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Počisti vse zaznamke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command will remove all the markers from the document as well as the "
"list of markers which is appended at the bottom of this menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz bo odstranil vse označevalce iz dokumenta in tudi seznam "
"označevalcev, ki je pripet na dnu tega elementa menija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &PgUp;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &PgUp;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnji</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:812
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the cursor to beginning of the first above line with a "
"bookmark. The menuitem text will include the line number and the first piece "
"of text on the line. This item is only available when there is a bookmark in "
"a line above the cursor."
msgstr ""
"S tem se kazalka premakne na začetek prve zgornje vrstice z zaznamkom. "
"Besedilo menijske postavke bo vsebovalo številko vrstice in prvi del "
"besedila v vrstici. Ta element je na voljo le, če je v vrstici nad kazalko "
"zaznamek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>PgDown</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>PgDown</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Zaznamki</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naprej</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will move the cursor to beginning of the next line with a bookmark. The "
"menuitem text will include the line number and the first piece of text on "
"the line. This item is only available when there is a bookmark in a line "
"below the cursor."
msgstr ""
"S tem se kazalka premakne na začetek naslednje vrstice z zaznamkom. Besedilo "
"menijske postavke bo vsebovalo številko vrstice in prvi del besedila v "
"vrstici. Ta element je na voljo le, če je v vrstici pod kazalko zaznamek."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of this menu, a list of bookmarks appears if any bookmarks are "
"available for this window."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu tega menija se prikaže seznam zaznamkov, če so za to okno na voljo "
"kateri koli zaznamki."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Read Only Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Način samo za branje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the current document to Read Only mode. This prevents any text addition "
"and any changes in the document formatting."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite trenutni dokument v način samo za branje. To prepreči kakršno koli "
"dodajanje besedila in kakršne koli spremembe v oblikovanju dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Mode</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Način</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the filetype scheme you prefer for the active document. This "
"overwrites the global filetype mode set in <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the "
"Filetypes tab for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite shemo vrste datoteke, ki vam je ljubša za aktivni dokument. To "
"prepiše globalni način vrste datoteke, nastavljen v <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> na zavihku Vrste datotek samo za vaš trenutni "
"dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Highlighting</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poudarjanje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the Highlighting scheme you prefer for the active document. This "
"overwrites the global highlighting mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite shemo označevanja, ki vam je ljubša za aktivni dokument. To prepiše "
"globalni način označevanja, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:881
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Indentation</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zamik</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the style of indentation you want for your active document. This "
"overwrites the global indentation mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite slog zamika, ki ga želite za svoj aktivni dokument. To prepiše "
"globalni način zamika, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Encoding</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Kodiranje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can overwrite the default encoding set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in the <guilabel>Open/Save</guilabel> page to set a different "
"encoding for your current document. The encoding you set here will be only "
"valid for your current document."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto kodiranje lahko prepišete v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> na strani <guilabel>Odpri/Shrani</guilabel>, da nastavite "
"drugačno kodiranje za vaš trenutni dokument. Kodiranje, ki ga nastavite "
"tukaj, bo veljavno samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>End of Line</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Konec vrstice</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred end of line mode for your active document. This "
"overwrites the global end of line mode set in <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> for your current document only."
msgstr ""
"Izberite želeni način konca vrstice za vaš aktivni dokument. To prepiše "
"globalni način konca vrstice, nastavljen v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> samo za vaš trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Add Byte Mark Order (BOM)</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Dodaj vrstni red oznak bajtov (BOM)</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checking this action you can explicitly add a byte order mark for unicode "
"encoded documents. The byte order mark (BOM) is a Unicode character used to "
"signal the endianness (byte order) of a text file or stream, for more "
"information see <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_Order_Mark"
"\">Byte Order Mark</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če označite to dejanje, lahko izrecno dodate oznako vrstnega reda bajtov za "
"dokumente, kodirane z Unicode. Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov (BOM) je znak "
"Unicode, ki se uporablja za signalizacijo endianness (vrstni red bajtov) "
"besedilne datoteke ali toka, za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_Order_Mark\" >Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Invoke Code Completion</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikliči dokončanje kode</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Manually invoke command completion, usually by using a shortcut bound to "
"this action."
msgstr ""
"Ročno prikličite dokončanje ukaza, običajno z uporabo bližnjice, vezane na "
"to dejanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Word Completion</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dokončanje besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Reuse Word Below</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>) and <guimenuitem>Reuse Word Above</"
"guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>8</keycap></"
"keycombo>) complete the currently typed text by searching for similar words "
"backward or forward from the current cursor position. <guimenuitem>Shell "
"Completion</guimenuitem> pops up a completion box with matching entries."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Znova uporabi besedo spodaj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>9</keycap></keycombo>) in <guimenuitem>Ponovno "
"uporabi besedo zgoraj</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo>) dokončajte trenutno vneseno besedilo z "
"iskanjem podobnih besed nazaj ali naprej od trenutnega položaja kazalca. "
"<guimenuitem>Dokončanje lupine</guimenuitem> odpre polje za dokončanje z "
"ujemajočimi se vnosi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell "
"Checking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Samodejno "
"preverjanje črkovanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem> is enabled, wrong "
"text is underlined in the document on-the-fly."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno <guimenuitem>Samodejno preverjanje črkovanja</guimenuitem>, "
"je napačno besedilo v dokumentu sproti podčrtano."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:975
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spelling...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Črkovanje ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>This initiates the spellchecking program - a program designed to "
"help the user catch and correct any spelling errors.</action> Clicking on "
"this entry will start the checker and bring up the speller dialog box "
"through which the user can control the process. There are four settings "
"lined up vertically in the center of the dialog with their corresponding "
"labels just to the left. Starting at the top they are:"
msgstr ""
"<action>S tem se zažene program za preverjanje črkovanja – program, zasnovan "
"tako, da uporabniku pomaga odkriti in popraviti morebitne črkovalne napake.</"
"action> S klikom na ta vnos se bo zagnal preverjevalnik in prikazalo se "
"pogovorno okno črkovalnika, prek katerega lahko uporabnik nadzira postopek . "
"Na sredini pogovornega okna so navpično poravnane štiri nastavitve z "
"ustreznimi oznakami na levi strani. Začenši na vrhu so:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unknown word:"
msgstr "Neznana beseda:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:994
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, the spellchecker indicates the word currently under consideration. "
"This happens when the checker encounters a word not in its dictionary - a "
"file containing a list of correctly spelled words against which it compares "
"each word in the editor."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj črkovalnik označuje besedo, ki je trenutno v obravnavi. To se zgodi, "
"ko preverjevalnik naleti na besedo, ki je ni v njegovem slovarju - datoteko, "
"ki vsebuje seznam pravilno črkovanih besed, s katerimi primerja vsako besedo "
"v urejevalniku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace with:"
msgstr "Zamenjaj z:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the checker has any similar words in its dictionary the first one will be "
"listed here. The user can accept the suggestion, type in his or her own "
"correction, or choose a different suggestion from the next box."
msgstr ""
"Če ima pregledovalnik podobne besede v svojem slovarju, bo prva navedena "
"tukaj. Uporabnik lahko sprejme predlog, vnese svoj popravek ali izbere drug "
"predlog iz naslednjega polja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid "Language:"
msgstr "Jezik:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed multiple dictionaries, here you can select which "
"dictionary/language should be used."
msgstr ""
"Če ste namestili več slovarjev, lahko tukaj izberete, kateri slovar/jezik "
"želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the right side of the dialog box are 6 buttons that allow the user to "
"control the spellcheck process. They are:"
msgstr ""
"Na desni strani pogovornega okna je 6 gumbov, ki uporabniku omogočajo nadzor "
"nad postopkom preverjanja črkovanja. To so:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1018
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add to Dictionary"
msgstr "Dodaj v slovar"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing this button adds the <guilabel>Unknown word </guilabel> to the "
"checker's dictionary. This means that in the future the checker will always "
"consider this word to be correctly spelled."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete ta gumb, dodate <guilabel>Neznano besedo </guilabel> v slovar "
"pregledovalnika. To pomeni, da bo pregledovalec v prihodnje to besedo vedno "
"štel za pravilno črkovano."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suggest"
msgstr "Predlagaj"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The checker may list here a number of possible replacements for the word "
"under consideration. Clicking on any one of the suggestions will cause that "
"word to be entered in the <guilabel>Replace with</guilabel> box, above."
msgstr ""
"Preverjevalec lahko tukaj navede številne možne zamenjave za obravnavano "
"besedo. Če kliknete katerega koli od predlogov, bo ta beseda vnesena v polje "
"<guilabel>Zamenjaj z</guilabel> zgoraj."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace"
msgstr "Zamenjaj"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button has the checker replace the word under consideration in the "
"document with the word in the <guilabel>Replace with</guilabel> box."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb ima preverjevalnik zamenjavo obravnavane besede v dokumentu z besedo "
"v polju <guilabel>Zamenjaj z</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1038
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace All"
msgstr "Zamenjaj vse"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button causes the checker to replace not only the current "
"<guilabel>Unknown word:</guilabel> but to automatically make the same "
"substitution for any other occurrences of this <guilabel>Unknown word</"
"guilabel> in the document."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb povzroči, da preverjevalnik zamenja ne samo trenutno "
"<guilabel>Neznano besedo:</guilabel>, temveč samodejno izvede isto zamenjavo "
"za vse druge pojavitve te <guilabel>Neznane besede</guilabel> v dokumentu."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1045
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore"
msgstr "Ignoriraj"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Activating this button will have the checker move on without making any "
"changes."
msgstr "Če aktivirate ta gumb, se bo dama premaknila naprej brez sprememb."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore All"
msgstr "Ignoriraj vse"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button tells the checker to do nothing with the current "
"<guilabel>Unknown word:</guilabel> and to pass over any other instances of "
"the same word."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb sporoča preverjevalniku, naj ne naredi ničesar s trenutno "
"<guilabel>Neznano besedo:</guilabel> in naj preskoči vse druge primere iste "
"besede."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This only applies to the current spellcheck run. If the checker is run again "
"later it will stop on this same word."
msgstr ""
"To velja samo za trenutno izvajanje preverjanja črkovanja. Če preverjalnik "
"pozneje znova zaženete, se bo ustavil pri tej isti besedi."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Three more buttons are located horizontally along the bottom of the "
"spellcheck dialog. They are:"
msgstr ""
"Še trije gumbi se nahajajo vodoravno na dnu pogovornega okna za preverjanje "
"črkovanja. To so:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1064
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Na pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid "This invokes the &kde; help system with the help page for this dialog."
msgstr ""
"To prikliče &kde; sistem pomoči s stranjo s pomočjo za to pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finished"
msgstr "Končano"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1071
#, no-c-format
msgid "This button ends the spellcheck process, and returns to the document."
msgstr "Ta gumb konča postopek preverjanja črkovanja in se vrne v dokument."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1076
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Prekliči"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button cancels the spellcheck process, all modifications are reverted, "
"and you will return to your document."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb prekliče postopek preverjanja črkovanja, vse spremembe so "
"razveljavljene in vrnili se boste v svoj dokument."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spelling (from cursor)...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Črkovanje (iz kazalca)...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This initiates the spellchecking program but it starts where your cursor is "
"instead of at the beginning of the document."
msgstr ""
"To zažene program za preverjanje črkovanja, vendar se začne tam, kjer je vaš "
"kazalec namesto na začetku dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1097
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spellcheck Selection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbira preverjanja črkovanja ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellchecks the current selection."
msgstr "Preveri črkovanje trenutne izbire."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1106
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Change Dictionary</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spremeni slovar</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a drop down box with all available dictionaries for spellchecking "
"at the bottom of the editor window. This allows easy switching of the "
"spellcheck dictionary &eg; for automatic spellcheck of text in different "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže spustno polje z vsemi razpoložljivimi slovarji za preverjanje "
"črkovanja na dnu okna urejevalnika. To omogoča preprosto preklapljanje med "
"slovarjem za preverjanje črkovanja &eg; za samodejno preverjanje črkovanja "
"besedila v različnih jezikih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1117
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clean Indentation</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Počisti zamik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This cleans the indentation for the current selection or for the line the "
"cursor is currently in. Cleaning the indentation ensures that all your "
"selected text follows the indentation mode you choose."
msgstr ""
"To počisti zamik za trenutni izbor ali za vrstico, v kateri je trenutno "
"kazalka. Čiščenje zamika zagotovi, da vse izbrano besedilo sledi izbranemu "
"načinu zamika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Align</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Poravnaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes a realign of the current line or selected lines using the indentation "
"mode and indentation settings in the document."
msgstr ""
"Povzroči ponovno poravnavo trenutne vrstice ali izbranih vrstic z uporabo "
"načina zamika in nastavitev zamika v dokumentu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Comment</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>D</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Komentar</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This adds one space to the beginning of the line where the text cursor is "
"located or to the beginning of any selected lines."
msgstr ""
"To doda en presledek na začetek vrstice, kjer se nahaja besedilni kazalec, "
"ali na začetek katere koli izbrane vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uncomment</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odkomentiraj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This removes one space (if any exist) from the beginning of the line where "
"the text cursor is located or from the beginning of any selected lines."
msgstr ""
"To odstrani en presledek (če obstaja) z začetka vrstice, kjer se nahaja "
"besedilna kazalka, ali z začetka katere koli izbrane vrstice."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uppercase</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Velike črke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put the selected text or the letter after the cursor in uppercase."
msgstr "Izbrano besedilo ali črko za kazalko postavite v velike črke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lowercase</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Male črke</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Put the selected text or the letter after the cursor in lowercase."
msgstr "Izbrano besedilo ali črko za kazalko vstavite z malimi črkami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Capitalize</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Napiši z "
"velikimi črkami</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Capitalize the selected text or the current word."
msgstr "Napiši izbrano besedilo ali trenutno besedo z veliko začetnico."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Join Lines</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Združi vrstice</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Joins the selected lines, or the current line and the line below with one "
"white space character as a separator. Leading/trailing white space on joined "
"lines is removed in the affected ends."
msgstr ""
"Združi izbrane vrstice ali trenutno vrstico in spodnjo vrstico z enim "
"presledkom kot ločilom. Začetni/zadnji prazen prostor na spojenih črtah je "
"odstranjen na prizadetih koncih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apply Word Wrap</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporabi prelom besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apply static word wrapping on all the document. That means that a new line "
"of text will automatically start when the current line exceeds the length "
"specified by the <guilabel>Wrap words at</guilabel> option in the Editing "
"tab in <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"Editor...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite statično prelivanje besed na celotnem dokumentu. To pomeni, da se "
"bo nova vrstica besedila samodejno začela, ko trenutna vrstica preseže "
"dolžino, določeno z možnostjo <guilabel>Prelomi besede v</guilabel> na "
"zavihku Urejanje v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem "
">Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <link linkend=\"katepart-pref-plugins\">plugin</link> Insert File is "
"enabled, you will find here an additional menu item <guimenuitem>Insert "
"File...</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če je <link linkend=\"katepart-pref-plugins\">vtičnik</link> Vstavi datoteko "
"omogočen, boste tukaj našli dodatno postavko menija <guimenuitem>Vstavi "
"datoteko ...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item opens a dialog whereby several different <link linkend="
"\"kredit_config\">settings</link> may be adjusted."
msgstr ""
"Ta menijski element odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem je mogoče prilagoditi "
"več različnih <link linkend=\"kredit_config\">nastavitev</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1261
#, no-c-format
msgid "The KrViewer Menu"
msgstr "Meni KrViewer"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Generic "
"viewer</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>G</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Generični "
"pregledovalnik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&krusader;'s internal viewer is actually part of &konqueror;, which can "
"basically view every file type viewable by &konqueror; (&eg; display "
"pictures, play music, show the content of an archive)."
msgstr ""
"Notranji pregledovalnik &krusader; je pravzaprav del &konqueror;-ja, ki si "
"lahko v bistvu ogleda vsako vrsto datoteke, ki jo lahko vidi &konqueror; "
"(&eg; prikaz slik, predvajanje glasbe, prikaz vsebine arhiva)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Text viewer</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pregledovalnik besedil</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1295
#, no-c-format
msgid "View the file in text mode."
msgstr "Oglejte si datoteko v besedilnem načinu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>H</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Hex viewer</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>H</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Šestnajstiški "
"pregledovalnik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid "View the file in hex mode."
msgstr "Oglejte si datoteko v hex načinu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lister</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lister</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fast text/hex viewer for huge filesizes, done by <link linkend=\"konfig-"
"general\">Krusader lister</link>."
msgstr ""
"Hiter pregledovalnik besedila/šestnajstiškega besedila za ogromne velikosti "
"datotek, ki ga izvaja <link linkend=\"konfig-general\">Krusader lister</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Text editor</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>E</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Urejevalnik "
"besedil</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit the file in text mode."
msgstr "Uredite datoteko v besedilnem načinu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Detach Tab</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odstrani "
"zavihek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detach browsing Tab and open in a new window."
msgstr "Odstrani zavihek za brskanje in odpri v novem oknu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl; <keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl; <keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>KrViewer</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes &krusader;'s viewer/editor window."
msgstr "Zapre okno pregledovalnika/urejevalnika &krusader;."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1387
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor Component Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija komponente urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains all pages related to the editor component of &kappname;. "
"Most of the settings here are defaults, they can be overridden by <link "
"linkend=\"katepart-pref-open-save-modes-filetypes\">defining a filetype</"
"link>, by <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/config-variables.html\">Document "
"Variables</ulink> or by changing them per document during an editing session."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vsebuje vse strani, povezane z urejevalnikom &kappname;. Večina "
"nastavitev tukaj je privzetih, lahko pa jih preglasite tako, da <link "
"linkend=\"katepart-pref-open-save-modes-filetypes\">določite vrsto datoteke</"
"link>, tako da <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/ config-variables.html"
"\">Spremenljivke dokumenta</ulink> ali tako, da jih spremenite za vsak "
"dokument med sejo urejanja."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "Videz"

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1397 viewer-editor.docbook:1685
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2079
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošno</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dynamic Word Wrap"
msgstr "Dinamični prelom besed"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, the text lines will be wrapped at the view border "
"on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo besedilne vrstice obrobljene ob meji pogleda "
"na zaslonu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dynamic word wrap indicators (if applicable)"
msgstr "Indikatorji dinamičnega preloma besed (če je primerno)"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose when the Dynamic word wrap indicators should be displayed, either "
"<guilabel>Off</guilabel>, <guilabel>Follow Line Numbers</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Always on</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kdaj naj bodo indikatorji dinamičnega preloma besed prikazani, "
"<guilabel>Izklopljeno</guilabel>, <guilabel>Sledi številkam vrstic</"
"guilabel> ali <guilabel>Vedno vključeno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Align dynamically wrapped lines to indentation depth:"
msgstr "Poravnajte dinamično zavite črte na globino vdolbine:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables the start of dynamically wrapped lines to be aligned vertically to "
"the indentation level of the first line. This can help to make code and "
"markup more readable."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča navpično poravnavo začetka dinamično zavitih vrstic na raven zamika "
"prve vrstice. To lahko pomaga narediti kodo in oznake bolj berljive."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, this allows you to set a maximum width of the screen, as a "
"percentage, after which dynamically wrapped lines will no longer be "
"vertically aligned. For example, at 50%, lines whose indentation levels are "
"deeper than 50% of the width of the screen will not have vertical alignment "
"applied to subsequent wrapped lines."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega vam to omogoča nastavitev največje širine zaslona v odstotkih, po "
"kateri dinamično zavite vrstice ne bodo več navpično poravnane. Na primer, "
"pri 50 % črtah, katerih stopnja zamika je globlja od 50 % širine zaslona, ne "
"bo uporabljena navpična poravnava za naslednje previte vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whitespace Highlighting"
msgstr "Označevanje presledkov"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlight tabulators"
msgstr "Označi tabulatorje"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will display a &raquo; symbol to indicate the presence of a tab "
"in the text."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo prikazal &raquo; simbol, ki označuje prisotnost zavihka v "
"besedilu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlight trailing spaces"
msgstr "Označite končne presledke"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will display dots to indicate the presence of extra whitespace at "
"the end of lines."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo prikazal pike, ki označujejo prisotnost dodatnega presledka "
"na koncu vrstic."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Advanced</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Napredno</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show indentation lines"
msgstr "Prikaži črte zamikov"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is checked, the editor will display vertical lines to help "
"identifying indent lines."
msgstr ""
"Če je to označeno, bo urejevalnik prikazal navpične črte, ki bodo pomagale "
"pri prepoznavanju zamikov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlight range between selected brackets"
msgstr "Označi obseg med izbranimi oklepaji"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is enabled, the range between the selected matching brackets will be "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Če je to omogočeno, bo obseg med izbranimi ujemajočimi se oklepaji označen."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1472
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Borders</title>"
msgstr "<title>Meje</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1476
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Borders</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Meje</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show folding markers (if available)"
msgstr "Pokaži zložljive oznake (če so na voljo)"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, the current view will display marks for code "
"folding, if code folding is available."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo v trenutnem pogledu prikazane oznake za "
"zlaganje kode, če je na voljo zlaganje kode."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1486
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show icon border"
msgstr "Pokaži obrobo ikone"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is checked, you will see an icon border on the left hand side. The "
"icon border shows bookmark signs for instance."
msgstr ""
"Če je to označeno, boste na levi strani videli obrobo ikone. Obroba ikone na "
"primer prikazuje znake zaznamkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show line numbers"
msgstr "Pokaži številke vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1494
#, no-c-format
msgid "If this is checked, you will see line numbers on the left hand side."
msgstr "Če je to označeno, boste na levi strani videli številke vrstic."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show scrollbar marks"
msgstr "Pokaži drsne oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked the current view will show marks on the vertical "
"scrollbar. These marks will for instance show bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo trenutni pogled prikazovali oznake na "
"navpičnem drsnem traku. Te oznake bodo na primer prikazale zaznamke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1509
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sort Bookmarks Menu"
msgstr "Meni Razvrsti zaznamke"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1514
#, no-c-format
msgid "By creation"
msgstr "Z ustvarjanjem"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each new bookmark will be added to the bottom, independently from where it "
"is placed in the document."
msgstr "Vsak nov zaznamek bo dodan na dno, ne glede na mesto v dokumentu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1520
#, no-c-format
msgid "By position"
msgstr "Po položaju"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1522
#, no-c-format
msgid "The bookmarks will be ordered by the line numbers they are placed at."
msgstr ""
"Zaznamki bodo razvrščeni po številkah vrstic, v katerih so postavljeni."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts &amp; Colors"
msgstr "Pisave &amp; Barve"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1536
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section of the dialog lets you configure all fonts and colors in any "
"color scheme you have, as well creating new schemes or deleting existing "
"ones. Each scheme has settings for colors, fonts and normal and highlight "
"text styles."
msgstr ""
"Ta del pogovornega okna vam omogoča konfiguracijo vseh pisav in barv v "
"kateri koli barvni shemi, ki jo imate, kot tudi ustvarjanje novih shem ali "
"brisanje obstoječih. Vsaka shema ima nastavitve za barve, pisave ter "
"običajne in poudarjene sloge besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; will preselect the currently active scheme for you, if you want "
"to work on a different scheme start by selecting that from the "
"<guilabel>Schema</guilabel> combobox. With the <guibutton>New</guibutton> "
"and <guibutton>Delete</guibutton> button you can create a new scheme or "
"delete existing ones."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; bo namesto vas vnaprej izbral trenutno aktivno shemo, če želite "
"delati na drugi shemi, začnite tako, da jo izberete v kombiniranem polju "
"<guilabel>Shema</guilabel>. Z gumboma <guibutton>Novo</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton> lahko ustvarite novo shemo ali izbrišete "
"obstoječe."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the page you can select the <guilabel>Default schema for "
"&kappname;</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu strani lahko izberete <guilabel>Privzeto shemo za &kappname;</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Barve"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1553
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Area Background"
msgstr "Ozadje območja besedila"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1559
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal text"
msgstr "Običajno besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default background for the editor area, it will be the dominant "
"color on the editor area."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeto ozadje za območje urejevalnika in bo prevladujoča barva na "
"območju urejevalnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selected text"
msgstr "Izbrano besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the background for selected text. The default is the global "
"selection color, as set in your &plasma; color preferences."
msgstr ""
"To je ozadje za izbrano besedilo. Privzeta je barva globalnega izbora, kot "
"je nastavljena v vašem &plasma; barvne nastavitve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1572
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current line"
msgstr "Trenutna linija"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the color for the current line. Setting this a bit different from the "
"Normal text background helps to keep focus on the current line."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo za trenutno vrstico. Če to nastavite nekoliko drugačno od "
"običajnega ozadja besedila, pomaga ohraniti fokus na trenutni vrstici."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1579
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmark"
msgstr "Zaznamek"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This combobox lets you set overlay colors for various mark types. The color "
"is mixed into the background color of a marked line, so that a line with "
"more marks or a marked line that is current has a background that is a mix "
"of more colors. The mark colors are also used if you enable display of "
"scrollbar marks."
msgstr ""
"To kombinirano polje vam omogoča nastavitev barv prekrivanja za različne "
"vrste oznak. Barva se vmeša v barvo ozadja označene črte, tako da ima črta z "
"več oznakami ali označena črta, ki je aktualna, ozadje, ki je mešanica več "
"barv. Barve oznak se uporabljajo tudi, če omogočite prikaz oznak drsnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional Elements"
msgstr "Dodatni elementi"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1596
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left border background"
msgstr "Ozadje leve obrobe"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used for the marks, line numbers and folding marker borders in "
"the left side of the editor view when they are displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za oznake, številke vrstic in robove pregibnih oznak "
"na levi strani pogleda urejevalnika, ko so prikazani."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1602
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line numbers"
msgstr "Številke vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to draw the line numbers on the left side of the view "
"when displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje številk vrstic na levi strani pogleda, ko "
"je prikazan."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bracket highlight"
msgstr "Označevanje oklepaja"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1608
#, no-c-format
msgid "This color is used to draw the background of matching brackets."
msgstr "Ta barva se uporablja za risanje ozadja ujemajočih se oklepajev."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1612
#, no-c-format
msgid "Word wrap markers"
msgstr "Oznake za prelom besed"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This color is used to draw a pattern to the left of dynamically wrapped "
"lines when those are aligned vertically, as well as for the static word wrap "
"marker."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje vzorca na levi strani dinamično zavitih "
"črt, ko so te poravnane navpično, kot tudi za statični marker za prelom "
"besed."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tab and space markers"
msgstr "Oznake zavihkov in presledkov"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1619
#, no-c-format
msgid "This color is used to draw white space indicators when enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ta barva se uporablja za risanje indikatorjev praznega prostora, ko je "
"omogočena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spelling mistake line"
msgstr "Vrstica črkovalne napake"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1624
#, no-c-format
msgid "sets the color of the line that is used to indicate spelling mistakes."
msgstr "nastavi barvo črte, ki se uporablja za označevanje črkovalnih napak."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can choose the font for the schema. You can choose from any font "
"available on your system, and set a default size. A sample text displays at "
"the bottom of the dialog, so you can see the effect of your choices."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete pisavo za shemo. Izbirate lahko med katero koli pisavo, "
"ki je na voljo v vašem sistemu, in nastavite privzeto velikost. Vzorčno "
"besedilo se prikaže na dnu pogovornega okna, tako da lahko vidite učinek "
"svojih izbir."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1644
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal Text Styles"
msgstr "Običajni slogi besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The normal text styles are inherited by the highlight text styles, allowing "
"the editor to present text in a very consistent way, for example comment "
"text is using the same style in almost all of the text formats that "
"&kappname; can highlight."
msgstr ""
"Običajni besedilni slogi so podedovani s poudarjenimi besedilnimi slogi, kar "
"omogoča urejevalniku, da predstavi besedilo na zelo dosleden način, na "
"primer besedilo komentarja uporablja isti slog v skoraj vseh oblikah "
"besedila, ki jih &kappname; lahko poudari."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1649 viewer-editor.docbook:1664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name in the list of styles is using the style configured for the item, "
"providing you with an immediate preview when configuring a style."
msgstr ""
"Ime na seznamu slogov uporablja slog, konfiguriran za element, kar vam "
"omogoča takojšen predogled, ko konfigurirate slog."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1652
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each style lets you select common attributes as well as foreground and "
"background colors. To unset a background color, rightclick to use the "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Vsak slog vam omogoča izbiro skupnih atributov ter barv ospredja in ozadja. "
"Če želite razveljaviti barvo ozadja, z desnim klikom uporabite kontekstni "
"meni."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1658
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlighting Text Styles"
msgstr "Označevanje besedilnih slogov"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can edit the text styles used by a specific highlight definition. "
"The editor preselects the highlight used by your current document. To work "
"on a different highlight, select one in the <guilabel>Highlight</guilabel> "
"combobox above the style list."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko urejate besedilne sloge, ki jih uporablja določena definicija "
"osvetlitve. Urejevalnik vnaprej izbere osvetlitev, ki jo uporablja vaš "
"trenutni dokument. Če želite delati na drugem poudarku, ga izberite v "
"kombiniranem polju <guilabel>Označi</guilabel> nad seznamom slogov."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each style lets you select common attributes as well as foreground and "
"background colors. To unset a background color, rightclick to use the "
"context menu. In addition you can see if a style is equal to the default "
"style used for the item, and set it to that if not."
msgstr ""
"Vsak slog vam omogoča izbiro skupnih atributov ter barv ospredja in ozadja. "
"Če želite razveljaviti barvo ozadja, z desnim klikom uporabite kontekstni "
"meni. Poleg tega lahko vidite, ali je slog enak privzetemu slogu, "
"uporabljenemu za element, in ga nastavite na to, če ni."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You will notice that many highlights contain other highlights represented by "
"groups in the style list. For example most highlights import the Alert "
"highlight, and many source code formats imports the Doxygen highlight. "
"Editing colors in those groups only affects the styles when used in the "
"edited highlight format."
msgstr ""
"Opazili boste, da številni poudarki vsebujejo druge poudarke, ki jih "
"predstavljajo skupine na seznamu slogov. Večina poudarkov na primer uvozi "
"poudarek opozorila, številni formati izvorne kode pa uvozijo poudarek "
"Doxygen. Urejanje barv v teh skupinah vpliva samo na sloge, če se "
"uporabljajo v urejenem formatu osvetlitve."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing"
msgstr "Urejanje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1689
#, no-c-format
msgid "Static Word Wrap"
msgstr "Statični prelom besed"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Word wrap is a feature that causes the editor to automatically start a new "
"line of text and move (wrap) the cursor to the beginning of that new line. "
"&kappname; will automatically start a new line of text when the current line "
"reaches the length specified by the <link linkend=\"katepart-pref-wrap-words-"
"at\">Wrap Words At:</link> option."
msgstr ""
"Prelom besed je funkcija, ki povzroči, da urejevalnik samodejno začne novo "
"vrstico besedila in premakne (prelomi) kazalec na začetek te nove vrstice. "
"&kappname; samodejno začne novo vrstico besedila, ko trenutna vrstica doseže "
"dolžino, določeno z možnostjo <link linkend=\"katepart-pref-wrap-words-at"
"\">Prelomi besede na:</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable static word wrap"
msgstr "Omogoči statični prelom besed"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1700
#, no-c-format
msgid "Turns static word wrap on or off."
msgstr "Vklopi ali izklopi statični prelom besed."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show static word wrap markers (if applicable)"
msgstr "Prikaži statične oznake za prelom besed (če je na voljo)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wrap words at:"
msgstr "Zavij besede na:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <link linkend=\"katepart-pref-word-wrap\">Enable static word wrap</"
"link> option is selected this entry determines the length (in characters) at "
"which the editor will automatically start a new line."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <link linkend=\"katepart-pref-word-wrap\">Omogoči "
"statični prelom besed</link>, ta vnos določa dolžino (v znakih), pri kateri "
"bo urejevalnik samodejno začel novo vrstico."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Misc"
msgstr "Razno"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1731
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove trailing spaces while editing"
msgstr "Odstranite končne presledke med urejanjem"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; will automatically eliminate extra spaces at the ends of lines of "
"text."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; bo samodejno odstranil dodatne presledke na koncih vrstic "
"besedila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1736
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto brackets"
msgstr "Avtomatski oklepaji"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the user types a left bracket ([, (, or {) &kappname; automatically "
"enters the right bracket (}, ), or ]) to the right of the cursor."
msgstr ""
"Ko uporabnik vnese levi oklepaj ([, ( ali {) &kappname; samodejno vnese "
"desni oklepaj (}, ) ali ]) desno od kazalke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1742
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy/Cut the current line if no selection"
msgstr "Kopiraj/izreži trenutno vrstico, če ni izbrane"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled and the text selection is empty, copy and cut "
"action are performed for the line of text at the actual cursor position."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena in je izbor besedila prazen, se dejanja kopiranja "
"in izrezovanja izvedejo za vrstico besedila na dejanskem položaju kazalke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow scrolling past the end of the document"
msgstr "Dovoli pomikanje čez konec dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you scroll past the end of the document. This can be used "
"to vertically centre the bottom of the document, or put it on top of the "
"current view."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča, da se pomaknete čez konec dokumenta. To lahko "
"uporabite za navpično centriranje dna dokumenta ali pa ga postavite na vrh "
"trenutnega pogleda."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1760
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursor &amp; Selection"
msgstr "Kazalka &amp; Izbira"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1765
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Cursor Movement"
msgstr "Premikanje kazalke besedila"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1769
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smart home and smart end"
msgstr "Pameten dom in pameten konec"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, pressing the home key will cause the cursor to skip white "
"space and go to the start of a line's text."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana, bo pritisk tipke Domov povzročil, da kazalec preskoči prazen "
"prostor in se premakne na začetek besedila vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1776
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wrap cursor"
msgstr "Prelomi kazalko"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When on, moving the insertion cursor using the &Left; and &Right; keys will "
"go on to previous/next line at beginning/end of the line, similar to most "
"editors."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vklopljeno, premikanje kazalca za vstavljanje z &Left; in &Right; "
"tipke se bodo premaknile v prejšnjo/naslednjo vrstico na začetku/koncu "
"vrstice, podobno kot pri večini urejevalnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When off, the insertion cursor cannot be moved left of the line start, but "
"it can be moved off the line end, which can be very handy for programmers. "
"When this option is chosen, moving the cursor with the arrow keys off the "
"end of a line (to the right) causes it to jump down to the beginning of the "
"next line. Likewise when the cursor is moved past the beginning of a line "
"(to the left) it jumps up to the end of the preceding line. When this option "
"is not selected, moving the cursor right past the end of a line merely "
"causes it to continue horizontally in the same line and trying to move it "
"left past the beginning does nothing."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izklopljen, kazalca za vstavljanje ni mogoče premakniti levo od "
"začetka vrstice, lahko pa ga premaknete s konca vrstice, kar je lahko zelo "
"priročno za programerje. Ko izberete to možnost, premikanje kazalca s "
"puščičnimi tipkami s konca vrstice (v desno) povzroči, da skoči navzdol na "
"začetek naslednje vrstice. Podobno, ko se kazalec premakne čez začetek "
"vrstice (v levo), skoči na konec prejšnje vrstice. Ko ta možnost ni izbrana, "
"premikanje kazalca desno čez konec vrstice samo povzroči, da se nadaljuje "
"vodoravno v isti vrstici, poskus premikanja levo čez začetek pa ne povzroči "
"nič."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1792
#, no-c-format
msgid "PageUp/PageDown moves cursor"
msgstr "PageUp/PageDown premakne kazalko"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option changes the behavior of the cursor when the user presses the "
"&PgUp; or &PgDn; key. If unselected the text cursor will maintain its "
"relative position within the visible text in &kappname; as new text becomes "
"visible as a result of the operation. So if the cursor is in the middle of "
"the visible text when the operation occurs it will remain there (except when "
"one reaches the beginning or end.) With this option selected, the first key "
"press will cause the cursor to move to either the top or bottom of the "
"visible text as a new page of text is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost spremeni obnašanje kazalke, ko uporabnik pritisne &PgUp; ali "
"&PgDn; ključ. Če ni izbran, bo besedilna kazalka ohranila svoj relativni "
"položaj znotraj vidnega besedila v &kappname; kot novo besedilo postane "
"vidno kot rezultat operacije. Torej, če je kazalka na sredini vidnega "
"besedila, ko se izvede operacija, bo ostal tam (razen ko dosežete začetek "
"ali konec.) Ko je izbrana ta možnost, bo prvi pritisk tipke povzročil, da se "
"kazalka premakne bodisi na vrh ali na dnu vidnega besedila, ko se prikaže "
"nova stran besedila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1805
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autocenter cursor (lines):"
msgstr "Samodejna sredinska kazalka (črte):"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the number of lines to maintain visible above and below the cursor when "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi število vrstic, ki naj ostanejo vidne nad in pod kazalko, kadar je "
"to mogoče."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Selection Mode"
msgstr "Način izbire besedila"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1820
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Normalno"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1822
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selections will be overwritten by typed text and will be lost on cursor "
"movement."
msgstr ""
"Izbire bo prepisalo vtipkano besedilo in bodo izgubljeni ob premikanju "
"kazalke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1827
#, no-c-format
msgid "Persistent"
msgstr "Vztrajno"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1829
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selections will stay even after cursor movement and typing."
msgstr "Izbire bodo ostale tudi po premikanju kazalke in tipkanju."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1840
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation"
msgstr "Zamik"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1845
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Indentation mode:"
msgstr "Privzeti način zamika:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the automatic indentation mode you want to use as default. It is "
"strongly recommended to use <userinput>None</userinput> or "
"<userinput>Normal</userinput> here, and use filetype configurations to set "
"other indentation modes for text formats like C/C++ code or &XML;."
msgstr ""
"Izberite način samodejnega zamika, ki ga želite uporabiti kot privzetega. "
"Zelo priporočljivo je, da tukaj uporabite <userinput>Brez</userinput> ali "
"<userinput>Normalno</userinput> in uporabite konfiguracije vrste datotek za "
"nastavitev drugih načinov zamika za formate besedila, kot sta koda C/C++ ali "
"&XML;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1855
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indent using"
msgstr "Uporaba zamika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1859
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabulators"
msgstr "Tabulatorji"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1861
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled the editor will insert tabulator characters when you "
"press the &Tab; key or use <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-autoindent."
"html\">automatic indentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to omogočeno, bo urejevalnik vstavil tabulatorske znake, ko pritisnete "
"gumb &Tab; tipko ali uporabite <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-"
"autoindent.html\">samodejno zamikanje</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1867
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spaces"
msgstr "Presledki"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1869
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled the editor will insert a calculated number of spaces "
"according to the position in the text and the <option>tab-width</option> "
"setting when you press the &Tab; key or use <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-"
"part-autoindent.html\">automatic indentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to omogočeno, bo urejevalnik vstavil izračunano število presledkov "
"glede na položaj v besedilu in nastavitev <option>širine zavihka</option>, "
"ko pritisnete gumb &Tab; tipko ali uporabite <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/"
"kate-part-autoindent.html\">samodejno zamikanje</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1876
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabulators and Spaces"
msgstr "Tabulatorji in presledki"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled, the editor will insert spaces as describe above when "
"indenting or pressing &Tab; at the beginning of a line, but insert "
"tabulators when the &Tab; key is pressed in the middle or end of a line."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to omogočeno, bo urejevalnik vstavil presledke, kot je opisano zgoraj, "
"ko zamika ali pritisne &Tab; na začetku vrstice, vendar vstavite "
"tabulatorje, ko &Tab; je tipka pritisnjena na sredini ali koncu vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1884
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tab width:"
msgstr "Širina zavihka:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This configures the number of spaces that are displayed in place of a "
"tabulator character."
msgstr ""
"To konfigurira število presledkov, ki so prikazani namesto znaka tabulatorja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1891
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation width:"
msgstr "Širina vdolbine:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1893
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The indentation width is the number of spaces which is used to indent a "
"line. If configured to indent using tabulators, a tabulator character is "
"inserted if the indentation is divisible by the tab width."
msgstr ""
"Širina zamika je število presledkov, ki se uporabljajo za zamik vrstice. Če "
"je konfiguriran za zamik z uporabo tabulatorjev, se znak tabulatorja vstavi, "
"če je zamik deljiv s širino zavihka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1903
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti zamika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1907
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep Extra Spaces"
msgstr "Ohrani dodatne prostore"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is disabled, changing the indentation level aligns a line to "
"a multiple of the width specified in <guilabel>Indentation width</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost onemogočena, sprememba stopnje zamika poravna črto na "
"večkratnik širine, določene v <guilabel>Širina zamika</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjust indentation of code pasted from the clipboard"
msgstr "Prilagodite zamik kode, prilepljene iz odložišča"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, pasted code from the clipboard is indented. "
"Triggering the <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem> action removes the "
"indentation."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, se prilepljena koda iz odložišča zamakne. Sprožitev "
"dejanja <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem> odstrani zamik."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1924
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Actions"
msgstr "Dejanja zamikov"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1928
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backspace key in leading blank space unindents"
msgstr "Tipka vračalka v začetni prazen prostor odstrani zamike"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1930
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Backspace; key decreases the indentation "
"level if the cursor is located in the leading blank space of a line."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost izbrana, se tipka &Backspace; tipka zmanjša stopnjo zamika, "
"če se kazalka nahaja na prvem praznem mestu vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1935
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tab key action (if no selection exists)"
msgstr "Dejanje tipke Tab (če ni izbire)"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want &Tab; to align the current line in the current code block like "
"in emacs, make &Tab; a shortcut to the action <guimenuitem>Align</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite &Tab; da poravnate trenutno vrstico v trenutnem bloku kode, kot v "
"emacsu, naredite &Tab; bližnjica do dejanja <guimenuitem >Poravnaj</"
"guimenuitem >."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1943
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always advance to the next tab position"
msgstr "Vedno se pomaknite na naslednji položaj zavihka"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key always inserts white space so that "
"the next tab position is reached. If the option <guilabel>Insert spaces "
"instead of tabulators</guilabel> on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab in "
"the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> page is enabled, spaces are inserted; "
"otherwise, a single tabulator is inserted."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost, se &Tab; tipka vedno vstavi prazen prostor, tako "
"da je dosežen naslednji položaj zavihka. Če je možnost <guilabel>Vstavi "
"presledke namesto tabulatorjev</guilabel> na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</"
"guilabel> na strani <guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel> omogočena, se presledki "
"vstavijo; drugače je vstavljen en tabulator."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1952
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always increase indentation level"
msgstr "Vedno povečajte stopnjo zamika"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key always indents the current line by "
"the number of character positions specified in <guilabel>Indentation width</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost, se &Tab; tipka vedno zamakne trenutno vrstico za "
"število položajev znakov, določenih v <guilabel>Širina zamika</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1960
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase indentation level if in leading blank space"
msgstr "Povečajte stopnjo zamika, če je na začetku prazen prostor"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key either indents the current line or "
"advances to the next tab position. If the insertion point is at or before "
"the first non-space character in the line, or if there is a selection, the "
"current line is indented by the number of character positions specified in "
"<guilabel>Indentation width</guilabel>. If the insertion point is located "
"after the first non-space character in the line and there is no selection, "
"white space is inserted so that the next tab position is reached: if the "
"option <guilabel>Insert spaces instead of tabulators</guilabel> on the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> tab in the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> page is "
"enabled, spaces are inserted; otherwise, a single tabulator is inserted."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost, se &Tab; tipka zamakne trenutno vrstico ali se "
"premakne na naslednji položaj zavihka. Če je točka vstavljanja na ali pred "
"prvim znakom, ki ni presledek v vrstici, ali če obstaja izbor, je trenutna "
"vrstica zamaknjena s številom položajev znakov, določenim v <guilabel>Širina "
"zamika</guilabel>. Če se točka vstavljanja nahaja za prvim znakom, ki ni "
"presledek v vrstici, in ni izbire, se vstavi prazen prostor, tako da je "
"dosežen naslednji položaj zavihka: če je možnost <guilabel>Vstavi presledke "
"namesto tabulatorjev</guilabel> na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> na "
"strani <guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel> je omogočeno, presledki so vstavljeni; "
"drugače je vstavljen en tabulator."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto Completion"
msgstr "Samodejno dokončanje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1989 viewer-editor.docbook:2020
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>General</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable auto completion"
msgstr "Omogoči samodejno dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:1995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, a word completion box automatically pops up during typing "
"showing a list of text entries to complete the current text under the cursor."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, se med tipkanjem samodejno pojavi polje za dokončanje "
"besed, ki prikazuje seznam besedilnih vnosov za dokončanje trenutnega "
"besedila pod kazalko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2005
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimal word length to complete"
msgstr "Minimalna dolžina besede za dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While typing text, the word completion searches for words in the document "
"starting with the already typed text. This option configures the minimal "
"amount of characters that are needed to make the word completion active and "
"pop up a completion box."
msgstr ""
"Med vnašanjem besedila dopolnjevanje besed išče besede v dokumentu, ki se "
"začnejo z že vnesenim besedilom. Ta možnost konfigurira minimalno število "
"znakov, ki so potrebni, da postane dopolnjevanje besed aktivno in se prikaže "
"okno za dopolnjevanje."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2017
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vi Input Mode"
msgstr "Vi vnosni način"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2024
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use VI input mode"
msgstr "Uporabi način vnosa VI"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, the vi input mode will be enabled when opening a new view. "
"You can still toggle the vi input mode on/off for a particular view in the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbran, bo način vnosa vi omogočen, ko odprete nov pogled. Še vedno "
"lahko vklopite/izklopite način vnosa vi za določen pogled v meniju "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2032
#, no-c-format
msgid "Let Vi commands override Kate shortcuts"
msgstr "Naj ukazi Vi preglasijo Kate bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, Vi commands will override &kappname;'s built-in commands. For "
"example: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> will "
"redo, and override the standard action (showing the search and replace "
"dialog)."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete, bodo ukazi Vi preglasili vgrajene ukaze &kappname;. Na primer: "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> bo ponovil in "
"preglasil standardno dejanje (prikaz pogovornega okna za iskanje in "
"zamenjavo)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2040
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide the Vi mode status bar"
msgstr "Skrij statusno vrstico načina Vi"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2042
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, an extra status bar will be used when the Vi input mode is "
"enabled. This status bar shows commands while they are being typed and "
"messages/errors produced by Vi commands."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočen način vnosa Vi, bo privzeto uporabljena dodatna vrstica "
"stanja. Ta statusna vrstica prikazuje ukaze med vnašanjem in sporočila/"
"napake, ki jih ustvarijo ukazi Vi."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2045
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checking this option will hide this extra status line."
msgstr "Če označite to možnost, boste skrili to dodatno statusno vrstico."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key Mapping"
msgstr "Preslikava ključev"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2053
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Key mapping is used to change the meaning of typed keys. This allows you to "
"move commands to other keys or make special keypresses for doing a series of "
"commands."
msgstr ""
"Preslikava tipk se uporablja za spreminjanje pomena vnesenih tipk. To vam "
"omogoča premikanje ukazov na druge tipke ali posebne pritiske tipk za "
"izvajanje niza ukazov."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2057
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Primer:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2058
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F2</keycap> -> <keycap>I--</keycap> &Esc;"
msgstr "<keycap>F2</keycap> -> <keycap>I--</keycap> &Esc;"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will prepend <keycap>I--</keycap> to a line when pressing <keycap>F2</"
"keycap>."
msgstr ""
"To bo dodalo <keycap>I--</keycap> pred vrstico, ko pritisnete <keycap>F2</"
"keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2068
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellcheck"
msgstr "Preverjanje črkovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2069
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These configuration options are described in the documentation for the "
"&systemsettings; module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/spellchecking\">Spell "
"Checker</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Te konfiguracijske možnosti so opisane v dokumentaciji za &systemsettings; "
"modul <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/spellchecking\">Črkovalnik</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2076
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open/Save"
msgstr "Odpri/Shrani"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2084
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Format"
msgstr "Format datoteke"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2089
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoding:"
msgstr "Kodiranje:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This defines the standard encoding to use to open/save files, if not changed "
"in the open/save dialog or by using a command line option."
msgstr ""
"To definira standardno kodiranje za odpiranje/shranjevanje datotek, če ni "
"spremenjeno v pogovornem oknu za odpiranje/shranjevanje ali z uporabo "
"možnosti ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoding Detection"
msgstr "Zaznavanje kodiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select an item from the drop down box, either to disable autodetection or "
"use <guilabel>Universal</guilabel> to enable autodetection for all "
"encodings. But as this may probably only detect utf-8/utf-16, selecting a "
"region will use custom heuristics for better results. If neither the "
"encoding chosen as standard above, nor the encoding specified in the open/"
"save dialog, nor the encoding specified on command line match the content of "
"the file, this detection will be run."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem polju izberite element, da onemogočite samodejno zaznavanje ali "
"uporabite <guilabel>Univerzalno</guilabel>, da omogočite samodejno "
"zaznavanje za vsa kodiranja. Ker pa to verjetno zazna samo utf-8/utf-16, bo "
"izbira regije za boljše rezultate uporabila hevristiko po meri. Če se niti "
"zgoraj izbrano standardno kodiranje, niti kodiranje, določeno v pogovornem "
"oknu za odpiranje/shranjevanje, niti kodiranje, določeno v ukazni vrstici, "
"ne ujemajo z vsebino datoteke, se bo zagnalo to zaznavanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fallback Encoding"
msgstr "Nadomestno kodiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This defines the fallback encoding to try for opening files if neither the "
"encoding chosen as standard above, nor the encoding specified in the open/ "
"save dialog, nor the encoding specified on command line match the content of "
"the file. Before this is used, an attempt will be made to determine the "
"encoding to use by looking for a byte order marker at start of file: if one "
"is found, the right unicode encoding will be chosen; otherwise encoding "
"detection will run, if both fail fallback encoding will be tried."
msgstr ""
"To definira nadomestno kodiranje za poskus odpiranja datotek, če se niti "
"kodiranje, izbrano kot standardno zgoraj, niti kodiranje, določeno v "
"pogovornem oknu za odpiranje/shranjevanje, niti kodiranje, določeno v ukazni "
"vrstici, ne ujemajo z vsebino datoteke. Preden se to uporabi, se bo "
"poskusilo določiti kodiranje za uporabo z iskanjem oznake vrstnega reda "
"bajtov na začetku datoteke: če je najden, bo izbrano pravo kodiranje "
"unicode; sicer se bo zagnalo zaznavanje kodiranja, če oba ne uspeta, se bo "
"poskusilo nadomestno kodiranje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2123
#, no-c-format
msgid "End of line:"
msgstr "Konec vrstice:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred end of line mode for your active document. You have "
"the choice between &UNIX;, DOS/&Windows; or Macintosh."
msgstr ""
"Izberite želeni način konca vrstice za vaš aktivni dokument. Izbirate lahko "
"med &UNIX;, DOS/&Windows; ali Macintosh."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic end of line detection"
msgstr "Samodejno zaznavanje konca vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this if you want the editor to autodetect the end of line type. The "
"first found end of line type will be used for the whole file."
msgstr ""
"Označite to, če želite, da urejevalnik samodejno zazna vrsto konca vrstice. "
"Prva najdena vrsta konca vrstice bo uporabljena za celotno datoteko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable byte order marker"
msgstr "Omogoči oznako vrstnega reda bajtov"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The byte order mark is a special sequence at the beginning of unicode "
"encoded documents. It helps editors to open text documents with the correct "
"unicode encoding. For more information see <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Byte_Order_Mark\">Byte Order Mark</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov je posebno zaporedje na začetku dokumentov, "
"kodiranih z Unicode. Urednikom pomaga odpreti besedilne dokumente s "
"pravilnim kodiranjem unicode. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_Order_Mark\">Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Cleanups on Load/Save"
msgstr "Samodejno čiščenje ob nalaganju/shranjevanju"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove trailing spaces"
msgstr "Odstranite končne presledke"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will automatically eliminate extra spaces at the ends of lines of "
"text while loading/saving the file."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo med nalaganjem/shranjevanjem datoteke samodejno odstranil "
"dodatne presledke na koncih vrstic besedila."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Advanced</title>"
msgstr "<title>Napredno</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder Config File"
msgstr "Konfiguracijska datoteka mape"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search depth for config file:"
msgstr "Globina iskanja konfiguracijske datoteke:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will search the given number of folder levels upwards for "
"&kappname; config file and load the settings line from it. Further "
"information about these hidden folder config files you find in the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/katepart/config-variables.html\">document variables section</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo po danem številu ravni mape navzgor iskal &kappname; "
"konfiguracijsko datoteko in iz nje naložite vrstico z nastavitvami. Dodatne "
"informacije o teh konfiguracijskih datotekah skritih map najdete v <ulink "
"url=\"help:/katepart/config-variables.html\">razdelku spremenljivk "
"dokumenta</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2193
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup on Save"
msgstr "Varnostno kopiraj ob shranjevanju"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Backing up on save will cause &kappname; to copy the disk file to &lt;"
"prefix&gt;&lt;filename&gt;&lt;suffix&gt; before saving changes. The suffix "
"defaults to <emphasis role=\"bold\">~</emphasis> and prefix is empty by "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Varnostno kopiranje ob shranjevanju bo povzročilo &kappname; da kopirate "
"diskovno datoteko v &lt;prefix&gt;&lt;filename&gt;&lt;suffix&gt; preden "
"shranite spremembe. Pripona je privzeto <emphasis role=\"bold\">~</"
"emphasis>, predpona pa je privzeto prazna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local files"
msgstr "Lokalne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this if you want backups of local files when saving."
msgstr ""
"Označite to, če želite pri shranjevanju varnostne kopije lokalnih datotek."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remote files"
msgstr "Oddaljene datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this if you want backups of remote files when saving."
msgstr ""
"Označite to, če želite pri shranjevanju varnostne kopije oddaljenih datotek."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prefix"
msgstr "Predpona"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the prefix to prepend to the backup file names."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite predpono, ki jo želite dodati pred imena datotek varnostne kopije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suffix"
msgstr "Pripona"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the suffix to add to the backup file names."
msgstr "Vnesite pripono, ki jo želite dodati imenom datotek varnostne kopije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disable swap file syncing"
msgstr "Onemogoči sinhronizacijo izmenjalne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; is able to recover (most of) what was written after last save in "
"case of a crash or power failure. A swap file (.swp.&lt;filename&gt;) is "
"created after the first editing action on a document. If the user doesn’t "
"save the changes and &kappname; crashes, the swap file remains on the disk. "
"When opening a file, &kappname; checks if there is a swap file for the "
"document and if it is, it asks the user whether he wants to recover the lost "
"data or not. The user has the possibility to view the differences between "
"the original file and the recovered one, too. The swap file is deleted after "
"every save and on normal exit."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; lahko obnovi (večino), kar je bilo napisano po zadnjem "
"shranjevanju v primeru zrušitve ali izpada električne energije. Izmenjalna "
"datoteka (.swp.&lt;ime datoteke&gt;) se ustvari po prvem dejanju urejanja "
"dokumenta. Če uporabnik ne shrani sprememb in &kappname; zruši, izmenjalna "
"datoteka ostane na disku. Ko odprete datoteko, &kappname; preveri ali "
"obstaja izmenjalna datoteka za dokument in če obstaja, vpraša uporabnika ali "
"želi obnoviti izgubljene podatke ali ne. Uporabnik ima možnost videti tudi "
"razlike med izvirno in obnovljeno datoteko. Izmenjalna datoteka se izbriše "
"po vsakem shranjevanju in ob običajnem izhodu."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; syncs the swap files on the disk every 15 seconds, but only if "
"they have changed since the last sync. The user can disable the swap files "
"syncing if he wants, by checking the <guilabel>Disable swap file syncing</"
"guilabel> box, but this can lead to more data loss."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; sinhronizira izmenjevalne datoteke na disku vsakih 15 sekund, "
"vendar le, če so bile od zadnje sinhronizacije spremenjene. Uporabnik lahko "
"onemogoči sinhronizacijo izmenjalnih datotek, če želi, tako da označi polje "
"<guilabel>Onemogoči sinhronizacijo izmenjalnih datotek</guilabel>, vendar "
"lahko to povzroči večjo izgubo podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modes &amp; Filetypes"
msgstr "Načini &amp; Vrste datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to override the default configuration for documents of "
"specified &MIME; types. When the editor loads a document, it will try if it "
"matches the file masks or &MIME; types for one of the defined filetypes, and "
"if so apply the variables defined. If more filetypes match, the one with the "
"highest priority will be used."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran vam omogoča, da preglasite privzeto konfiguracijo za dokumente "
"določenega &MIME; vrste. Ko urejevalnik naloži dokument, bo poskusil, ali se "
"ujema z datotečnimi maskami ali &MIME; vrste za eno od definiranih vrst "
"datotek, in če je tako, uporabite definirane spremenljivke. Če se ujema več "
"vrst datotek, bo uporabljena tista z najvišjo prioriteto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2259
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filetype:"
msgstr "Vrsta datoteke:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2260 viewer-editor.docbook:2280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filetype with the highest priority is the one displayed in the first "
"drop down box. If more filetypes were found, they are also listed."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta datoteke z najvišjo prioriteto je tista, ki je prikazana v prvem "
"spustnem polju. Če je bilo najdenih več vrst datotek, so tudi te navedene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2265
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>New</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Novo</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to create a new filetype. After you click on this button, the "
"fields below get empty and you can fill the properties you want for the new "
"filetype."
msgstr ""
"To se uporablja za ustvarjanje nove vrste datoteke. Ko kliknete ta gumb, se "
"spodnja polja izpraznijo in lahko izpolnite lastnosti, ki jih želite za novo "
"vrsto datoteke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2271
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove an existing filetype, select it from the drop down box and press "
"the Delete button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti obstoječo vrsto datoteke, jo izberite v spustnem meniju "
"in pritisnite gumb Izbriši."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties of <replaceable>current filetype</replaceable>"
msgstr "Lastnosti <replaceable>trenutne vrste datoteke</replaceable>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name:"
msgstr "Ime:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the filetype will be the text of the corresponding menu item. "
"This name is displayed in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Filetypes</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Ime vrste datoteke bo besedilo ustrezne menijske postavke. To ime je "
"prikazano v <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vrste datotek</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Section:"
msgstr "Razdelek:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The section name is used to organize the file types in menus. This is also "
"used in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Filetypes</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ime razdelka se uporablja za organiziranje vrst datotek v menijih. To se "
"uporablja tudi v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Vrste datotek</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variables:"
msgstr "Spremenljivke:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This string allows you to configure &kappname;'s settings for the files "
"selected by this &MIME; type using &kappname; variables. You can set almost "
"any configuration option, such as highlight, indent-mode, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Ta niz vam omogoča, da konfigurirate nastavitve &kappname; za datoteke, ki "
"jih izbere ta &MIME; tipkajte z &kappname; spremenljivke. Nastavite lahko "
"skoraj vse možnosti konfiguracije, kot so osvetlitev, način zamika &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> to see a list of all available variables "
"and their descriptions. Select the checkbox on the left to enable a "
"particular variable and then set the value of the variable on the right. "
"Some variables provide a drop-down box to select possible values from while "
"others require you to enter a valid value manually."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> za ogled seznama vseh razpoložljivih "
"spremenljivk in njihovih opisov. Izberite potrditveno polje na levi, da "
"omogočite določeno spremenljivko, nato pa nastavite vrednost spremenljivke "
"na desni. Nekatere spremenljivke ponujajo spustno polje za izbiro možnih "
"vrednosti, druge pa zahtevajo, da veljavno vrednost vnesete ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For complete information on these variables, see <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/"
"config-variables.html\">Configuring with Document Variables</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za popolne informacije o teh spremenljivkah glejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"katepart/config-variables.html\">Konfiguriranje s spremenljivkami dokumenta</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlighting:"
msgstr "Označevanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you create a new file type, this drop down box allows you to select a "
"filetype for highlighting."
msgstr ""
"Če ustvarite novo vrsto datoteke, vam ta spustni meni omogoča izbiro vrste "
"datoteke za označevanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Mode:"
msgstr "Način zamika:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2322
#, no-c-format
msgid "The drop down box specifies the indentation mode for new documents."
msgstr "Spustno polje določa način zamika za nove dokumente."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2327
#, no-c-format
msgid "File extensions:"
msgstr "Pripone datotek:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wildcards mask allows you to select files by filename. A typical mask "
"uses an asterisk and the file extension, for example <filename>*.txt; *."
"text</filename>. The string is a semicolon-separated list of masks."
msgstr ""
"Maska nadomestnih znakov omogoča izbiro datotek po imenu datoteke. Tipična "
"maska uporablja zvezdico in pripono datoteke, na primer <filename>*.txt; *."
"text</filename>. Niz je s podpičjem ločen seznam mask."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2334
#, no-c-format
msgid "&MIME; types:"
msgstr "&MIME; vrste:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays a wizard that helps you easily select &MIME; types."
msgstr "Prikaže čarovnika, ki vam pomaga enostavno izbrati &MIME; vrste."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Priority:"
msgstr "Prednost:"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets a priority for this file type. If more than one file type selects the "
"same file, the one with the highest priority will be used."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi prednost za to vrsto datoteke. Če več kot ena vrsta datoteke izbere "
"isto datoteko, bo uporabljena tista z najvišjo prioriteto."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Download Highlighting Files..."
msgstr "Prenos datotek za označevanje ..."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to download new or updated syntax highlight descriptions "
"from the &kappname; website."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, če želite prenesti nove ali posodobljene opise poudarkov "
"sintakse iz datoteke &kappname; Spletna stran."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extensions"
msgstr "Razširitve"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> tab lists all available plugins and you can "
"check those you want to use. Click on the <guibutton>Information</guibutton> "
"button to open the <guilabel>About</guilabel> dialog of this plugin."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel> navaja vse razpoložljive vtičnike in "
"označite lahko tiste, ki jih želite uporabiti. Kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Informacije</guibutton>, da odprete pogovorno okno <guilabel>O</"
"guilabel> tega dodatka."

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a configurable plugin is checked, the <guibutton>Configure</guibutton> "
"button is enabled and you can click it in order to configure the highlighted "
"plugin."
msgstr ""
"Ko je nastavljiv vtičnik označen, je gumb <guibutton>Konfiguriraj</"
"guibutton> omogočen in ga lahko kliknete, da konfigurirate označeni vtičnik."

#. Tag: title
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2370
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor Component Plugins"
msgstr "Vtičniki komponent urejevalnika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2379
#, no-c-format
msgid "AutoBrace"
msgstr "AutoBrace"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The autobrace plugin supersedes the &kappname; internal <quote>Auto "
"Brackets</quote> feature. It automatically inserts a closing brace <keycap>}"
"</keycap> at the beginning of the next line after ending a line with an "
"opening one <keycap>{</keycap> and pressing the &Enter; key."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik autobrace nadomesti &kappname; notranja funkcija <quote>Samodejni "
"oklepaji</quote>. Samodejno vstavi oklepaj <keycap>}</keycap> na začetek "
"naslednje vrstice, potem ko konča vrstico z začetnim <keycap>{</keycap> in "
"pritisne &Enter; ključ."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data Tools"
msgstr "Podatkovna orodja"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables data tools like thesaurus and spell check (if installed). Data tools "
"are only available when text is selected, or when the &RMB; is clicked over "
"a word. If no data tools are offered even when text is selected, you need to "
"install them. If this plugin is enabled and data tools are installed, "
"additional items appear at the end of the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča podatkovna orodja, kot sta tezaver in preverjanje črkovanja (če je "
"nameščeno). Podatkovna orodja so na voljo le, ko je izbrano besedilo ali ko "
"&RMB; klikne na besedo. Če podatkovna orodja niso na voljo, tudi ko je "
"besedilo izbrano, jih morate namestiti. Če je ta vtičnik omogočen in so "
"nameščena podatkovna orodja, se na koncu kontekstnega menija prikažejo "
"dodatni elementi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2401
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporter"
msgstr "Izvoznik"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command allows you to export the current document with all highlighting "
"information into a &HTML; document using <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Export as &HTML;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"Additionally you can use <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Copy as &HTML;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to copy the currently "
"selected text as &HTML; to the system clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz vam omogoča izvoz trenutnega dokumenta z vsemi informacijami o "
"označevanju v &HTML; dokument z uporabo <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvozi kot &HTML;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Poleg "
"tega lahko uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj kot &HTML;</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za kopiranje "
"trenutno izbranega besedila kot &HTML; v sistemsko odložišče."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2415
#, no-c-format
msgid "IconInserter"
msgstr "Vstavljalec ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The icon inserter plugin is only of use for &kde; developers: It adds an "
"item <guimenuitem>Insert KIcon-Code</guimenuitem> into the context menu of "
"the editor. If activated, the &plasma;'s icon chooser opens (showing "
"application icons, action icons &etc;..). If you click on it, the file name "
"without file extension will be inserted as text. Useful only for setting "
"icons via &kde-frameworks; through the KIcon() class."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik za vstavljanje ikon je uporaben samo za &kde; razvijalci: doda "
"element <guimenuitem>Vstavi KIcon-Code</guimenuitem> v kontekstni meni "
"urejevalnika. Če je aktivirano, se odpre izbirnik ikon &plasma; (prikazuje "
"ikone aplikacij, ikone dejanj &etc;). Če kliknete nanjo, bo ime datoteke "
"brez datotečne pripone vstavljeno kot besedilo. Uporabno samo za nastavitev "
"ikon prek &kde-frameworks; prek razreda KIcon()."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2424
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insane (not ZEN) &HTML; coding (light edition)"
msgstr "Noro (ne ZEN) &HTML; kodiranje (lahka izdaja)"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A plugin, which does zen-coding like selector completion. For more "
"information see <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zen_Coding\"> Zen "
"Coding</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik, ki kodira zen, kot je dokončanje izbirnika. Za več informacij "
"glejte <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zen_Coding\"> Kodiranje "
"Zen</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2430
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert File"
msgstr "Vstavi datoteko"

#. Tag: para
#: viewer-editor.docbook:2431
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin allows you to insert any readable file at the cursor position. "
"If enabled, the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu has an additional menu item "
"<guimenuitem>Insert File</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik vam omogoča vstavljanje katere koli berljive datoteke na položaj "
"kazalke. Če je omogočeno, ima meni <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> dodaten "
"menijski element <guimenuitem>Vstavi datoteko</guimenuitem>."
